Invocation Name: project management flashcards
des:
Alexa can help you learn P M P terms and definitions for your P M P Exam. You can review the flash cards and then test your knowledge. At any point you can say "Alexa, review mode" to switch to review or say "Alexa, test mode" to start a test. You can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next card. At any point during the test, you can say "Alexa, what's my score" to get your current test score.
Please do not forget to join PM Masterclass Page on Facebook. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
